<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> lewffe <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        als <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> in <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> reiche
                        sind, und begert, ob wir davon ihts <expan>west<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hört<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz wir ew das
                            <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>liezze<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Nu hören noch wissen wir czü disen
                                <expan>czeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von sölichen lewffen kein
                                <expan>eige<ex>n</ex>schaft</expan>, <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        man sagt lantmansweise, daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> künig
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und <expan>marchg<ex>ra</ex>f</expan> Jost
                                <expan>beyeinand<ex>er</ex></expan> czü Ofen sein. Ob
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> also sey <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> wie
                            <add>es</add> sich anslahen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, des
                                <expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan> wir nicht
                            <expan>gewisse<ex>n</ex></expan>. Wer <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz
                        wir fürbas iht eigenlichs erfüren, daz uns dewcht, daz ew czü
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, das <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewr
                                <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        ob ir <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>den lewffen</add> iht eigenlichs erfürt, daz ir uns das auch
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wöllet als vil
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> füglich sey. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        in die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Vincencii.</ab>
</div>
